{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM08_070.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x31,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "...Hey, Plachta? There's something I wanted to ask you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "What is it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "You know, you always look really sad whenever you talk about Luard."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I wanted to know why... Will you tell me?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "...I see, I appeared that way?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "While there are many things I wish to remember yet can't, this is one thing I'd like to forget, yet can't..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Plachta..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "It's likely because... Luard was once my friend."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "He was an irreplaceable friend and someone who researched alchemy with me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Huh, you and Luard were from the same village?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Yes... He might be different now, but he wasn't always like that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "You asked me before why I started using alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Oh, yeah. I remember asking that. You kept saying it was a secret..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Luard and I once studied alchemy together, for the same goal."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "That was to bring people happiness and prosperity through alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Wait, that's..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Yes... The same reason as you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I was a little embarrassed at the time you asked, so I ended up hiding it..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "In the past, Luard and I had the same dreams as you, and researched alchemy for that purpose."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I didn't know..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "...However, Luard has forgotten that purpose."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Alchemy research was simply a means to reach our goal, but that means became his goal instead."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "...Hey, Plachta? What do you want to do about Luard?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "I need to kill him, with my own hands, no matter what it takes. Just like I did in the past."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Luard can't be left alone while he continues researching Ablation Alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "...Really?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "...What?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Do you really want to kill Luard? Are you really thinking that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "I..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "I see you remembered my wish. To make everyone happy using alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "And of course, that \"everyone\" includes you too, Plachta."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Plachta, if you killed Luard... Would you really be happy?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Is that really what you want?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "...No, it isn't."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x21,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "He may have changed, but Luard was still my friend."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "We had the same dreams, and researched alchemy together. He was an irreplaceable friend."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x22,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "Of course I wouldn't want to kill him!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x23,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "But there's no other way! If I leave Luard as he is, then..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "...Hey, Plachta. We should try to persuade Luard together."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "Persuade him...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, we need to make him understand that Ablation Alchemy is dangerous."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "He had the same dreams as you before, right? Then it should be fine. I know he'll understand."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2e,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "msg_string": "We need to search for a way for everyone to be happy together. Okay?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2c,
            "msg_string": "It seems you're even more serious and straightforward about your dream than me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2d,
            "msg_string": "Thank you. I'll try a little harder to see my dream through as well."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2e,
            "msg_string": "Let's persuade Luard together."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2f,
            "msg_string": "To be honest, there's little hope of success. But we need to do everything we can."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x30,
            "msg_string": "Yeah... That's right! Let's do this, together!"
        }
    ]
}